08:10.417 --> 08:12.125
This guy-- He has stiffed
his workers

08:12.208 --> 08:14.792
every step along the way
in the hotel industry.

08:14.875 --> 08:18.625
He's a conman
who got away with it
for decades.

08:18.709 --> 08:20.709
-And now he's--
-He's not gonna get away with is
